{"word":"προστάσσω","slug":"προστάσσω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>προστάσσω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πρός\">πρός</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:τάσσω\">τάσσω</a></el>] ‘give authoritative directive’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ref.\">ref.</a> to course of action, <b>enjoin, order, prescribe <a href='B:470 1:24'>Mt 1:24</a>; <a href='B:470 8:4'>8:4</a>; <a href='B:480 1:44'>Mk 1:44</a>; <a href='B:510 10:33'>Ac 10:33</a>, <a href='B:510 10:48'>48</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ref.\">ref.</a> to determination of periods, either of human history or of seasons, <b>appoint, prescribe <a href='B:510 17:26'>Ac 17:26</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:προσρήγνυμι/προσρήσσω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:προστάτις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}